section.section:
Unless licensed by the Administration under this title, a person may not provide the following services to an individual with developmental disability or to a recipient of individual support services, as defined in § 7-901 of this title:
Day habilitation services;
Residential services;
Services coordination;
Vocational services;
More than 1 family support service, as defined in § 7-701 of this title;
More than 1 individual support service; and
More than 1 community supported living arrangements service, as defined in § 7-709 of this title.
